WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 25]

02:00.840 --> 02:02.100
You've finally come,

02:02.510 --> 02:03.410
my brother.

02:04.480 --> 02:04.900
Chi Wen.

02:06.710 --> 02:07.260
I'm here.

02:09.950 --> 02:12.340
You are our long-awaited kin

02:13.560 --> 02:14.930
and the last hope

02:14.930 --> 02:16.420
we have left for the world.

02:16.840 --> 02:17.580
What a pity.

02:18.800 --> 02:20.900
We won't be able to watch you grow up

02:21.520 --> 02:23.460
and transform into a dragon.

02:28.910 --> 02:29.690
I'm sorry.

02:31.190 --> 02:31.970
I'm sorry.

02:33.790 --> 02:34.560
For what?

02:37.630 --> 02:39.060
The last Dragon Deity's Power

02:41.000 --> 02:41.740
has dissipated.

02:43.630 --> 02:45.090
I can't be a dragon anymore.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.020
Besides,

02:50.240 --> 02:52.060
I still have fragments of Jiu Ying in me.

02:53.840 --> 02:55.650
He could manipulate me at any time.

02:59.630 --> 03:00.810
Perhaps

03:01.360 --> 03:03.090
this is fate.

03:04.120 --> 03:05.300
You can't turn into a dragon.

03:05.910 --> 03:08.060
But Jiu Ying can't kill me either.

03:09.080 --> 03:10.340
He is forever

03:10.340 --> 03:12.370
trapped in this dragon body.

03:14.840 --> 03:15.740
Is that it?

03:16.710 --> 03:18.420
You think I'll give up?

03:19.120 --> 03:20.180
Chi Wen.

03:20.310 --> 03:21.690
You're so naive.

03:40.590 --> 03:41.060
Chi Wen.

03:42.430 --> 03:43.090
Are you alright?

03:44.960 --> 03:45.620
I'm fine.

03:46.840 --> 03:47.490
Where's Ji Ling?

03:48.680 --> 03:50.180
Why didn't he come with you?

03:50.520 --> 03:52.620
He's the Dragon Deity we picked.

03:53.150 --> 03:54.930
I haven't seen him for a long time.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.060
Is he alright?

04:00.360 --> 04:01.930
Ji Ling is at the Shilin Sect.

04:03.750 --> 04:06.490
He was originally a little fox at the foot of South Mountain,

04:06.870 --> 04:07.770
all carefree.

04:08.400 --> 04:09.560
But he swallowed

04:09.560 --> 04:11.060
my dragon scale by mistake

04:11.840 --> 04:13.060
and shouldered a burden

04:13.060 --> 04:14.860
too heavy for him.

04:16.710 --> 04:17.580
I can see now.

04:19.520 --> 04:20.220
I can see now.

04:21.920 --> 04:22.660
What a surprise.

04:22.830 --> 04:24.060
The dragon scale

04:24.360 --> 04:25.130
didn't kill me,

04:25.630 --> 04:26.980
and cured my eyes instead.

04:30.750 --> 04:31.810
It also surprised me

04:32.480 --> 04:33.570
that it was you, little fox,

04:33.570 --> 04:34.810
who swallowed my dragon scale.

04:36.720 --> 04:37.620
Master Chi Wen,

04:37.870 --> 04:38.570
you remember me?

04:40.870 --> 04:41.570
Of course.

04:44.510 --> 04:46.250
Why did you swallow my dragon scale?

04:47.600 --> 04:48.660
I heard

04:48.950 --> 04:50.660
that it was a deadly mission

04:50.950 --> 04:52.490
and thought it would kill me.

04:53.000 --> 04:53.980
That's why I took it.

04:56.480 --> 04:57.740
He's a good man.

04:58.720 --> 04:59.930
I owe him my life.

05:05.360 --> 05:06.860
Maybe it was destined

05:07.750 --> 05:08.980
by heaven.

05:11.870 --> 05:12.450
Little fox.

05:14.310 --> 05:15.370
Do you have a name?

05:17.390 --> 05:18.100
From now on,

05:19.310 --> 05:20.540
let's call you Ji Ling.

05:22.630 --> 05:23.690
Ji Ling?

05:26.830 --> 05:27.660
Ji Ling.

05:30.040 --> 05:30.780
What a nice name.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.450
I have a name.

05:33.870 --> 05:35.450
Master Chi Wen gave me a name.

05:40.160 --> 05:40.930
Master Chi Wen,

05:41.750 --> 05:42.620
does this name

05:43.600 --> 05:44.890
carry a specific meaning?

05:46.390 --> 05:47.660
I heard

05:47.830 --> 05:49.060
that names carry meanings

05:49.600 --> 05:50.540
in the mortal world.

05:52.630 --> 05:53.980
Whoever swallows my dragon scale

05:54.480 --> 05:56.620
becomes a vessel for my spirit.

05:57.920 --> 05:59.420
Ji Ling, a spirit vessel.

06:10.430 --> 06:11.490
Aren't you afraid?

06:17.000 --> 06:18.370
If you hadn't

06:18.390 --> 06:19.620
saved me,

06:20.160 --> 06:21.330
I would have died.

06:22.270 --> 06:23.540
Why would I be scared

06:23.870 --> 06:25.100
to be your spirit vessel

06:25.600 --> 06:26.490
to save the world?

06:28.270 --> 06:29.370
I didn't expect

06:29.950 --> 06:31.450
that a little fox could

06:31.510 --> 06:32.570
do such a great thing.

06:35.920 --> 06:37.010
So Ji Ling

06:37.310 --> 06:38.740
was a vessel for your spirit.

06:40.600 --> 06:41.570
Then why did you

06:42.000 --> 06:43.420
choose to stay here?

06:43.800 --> 06:44.810
Out of sympathy.

06:46.160 --> 06:48.250
Yuan Wuhuo was doomed.

06:48.870 --> 06:50.130
But Ji Ling showed up

06:50.130 --> 06:51.490
unexpectedly.

06:52.630 --> 06:54.330
I couldn't bear to take the life

06:54.330 --> 06:56.100
of a kind creature at will.

06:57.160 --> 06:59.100
So we changed our plans.

06:59.270 --> 07:01.100
You made Ji Ling the "Dragon Deity".

07:02.480 --> 07:03.010
Didn't you?

07:03.390 --> 07:04.060
Yes.

07:05.920 --> 07:07.330
No one needs to be sacrificed.

07:07.950 --> 07:09.100
I have another way.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.000
Just lend me

07:12.000 --> 07:12.860
your demon power.

07:13.270 --> 07:14.570
I have plans

07:14.950 --> 07:15.780
about how to regain

07:16.120 --> 07:17.180
the Dragon Deity's Power.

07:20.000 --> 07:22.370
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity.

07:41.060 --> 07:43.260
♪Moonlight falters♪

07:43.860 --> 07:46.380
♪Spreading in silence♪

07:47.820 --> 07:51.300
♪Candles burn through our farewells♪

07:53.700 --> 07:55.900
♪Trapped in this body♪

07:56.580 --> 07:59.420
♪This borrowed halo♪

08:00.300 --> 08:04.380
♪Tears unshed, pain untold...♪

08:08.870 --> 08:10.980
I can't go on fooling around.

08:14.040 --> 08:15.330
It's time to grow up.

08:18.160 --> 08:20.180
Goodbye, little fox.

08:23.680 --> 08:24.620
I'll miss you.

08:25.020 --> 08:27.860
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

08:28.220 --> 08:31.020
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

08:31.180 --> 08:33.900
♪As I drift farther away♪

08:34.420 --> 08:37.340
♪I won't wipe my tears dry♪

08:37.700 --> 08:40.500
♪Afraid the sorrow fades too light♪

08:44.220 --> 08:46.660
♪No more longing♪

08:49.140 --> 08:51.860
♪Forget me not, forget me not♪

08:52.180 --> 08:55.340
♪You and I made a promise♪

08:55.500 --> 08:57.940
♪They laugh at me for going mad♪

08:58.380 --> 09:01.180
♪So what if I have?♪

09:01.820 --> 09:04.780
♪Miss me not, miss me not♪

09:04.980 --> 09:07.980
♪When heavy snow falls on the frozen river♪

09:08.180 --> 09:10.540
♪Even the wind will say♪

09:10.940 --> 09:15.940
♪It was never here♪

09:21.480 --> 09:22.570
How come

09:22.960 --> 09:25.020
you're carrying a fragrance out of nowhere?

09:26.670 --> 09:28.180
I bathe with only water and eat vegetarian.

09:28.750 --> 09:29.930
There can't be a fragrance.

09:31.480 --> 09:32.610
There is.

09:33.150 --> 09:34.660
But this smell

09:34.910 --> 09:36.730
makes people sad,

09:37.630 --> 09:40.260
as if they're hollowed out.

09:46.750 --> 09:47.900
Autumn days are bleak.

09:48.360 --> 09:49.930
The golden-scale wood

09:50.600 --> 09:51.780
is losing all its leaves.

09:52.630 --> 09:53.930
The branches look empty.

09:57.240 --> 09:58.690
That's why you have the delusion.

10:01.120 --> 10:02.090
If people

10:02.720 --> 10:04.300
can live for 100

10:05.870 --> 10:08.180
or 1000 years

10:08.750 --> 10:09.850
like trees,

10:11.670 --> 10:12.810
that would be nice.

10:23.630 --> 10:24.420
Not really.

10:26.120 --> 10:26.900
Trees

10:28.270 --> 10:29.140
are too lonely.

10:30.960 --> 10:31.900
For centuries,

10:32.790 --> 10:33.840
they had to stay put

10:33.840 --> 10:35.060
in one place.

10:37.790 --> 10:38.810
That's right.

10:40.510 --> 10:41.540
Little fox.

10:42.750 --> 10:44.330
You swallowed the dragon scale

10:44.670 --> 10:46.090
and obtained immortality.

10:47.000 --> 10:48.540
But you're neither a human

10:49.150 --> 10:50.330
nor a demon,

10:52.790 --> 10:54.140
without a single kin.

10:55.480 --> 10:57.780
You became

10:57.840 --> 10:59.690
the loneliest outlier in the world,

11:00.550 --> 11:02.570
and you carry the gravest

11:03.510 --> 11:05.500
and most hopeless mission,

11:06.750 --> 11:08.810
trapped in this lonely courtyard.

11:11.080 --> 11:12.690
I'm sorry.

11:16.120 --> 11:17.090
I don't have kin,

11:18.600 --> 11:19.570
but I have friends.

11:21.440 --> 11:22.420
They are by my side.

11:22.960 --> 11:23.570
Aren't they?

11:26.550 --> 11:27.900
But people around you

11:30.120 --> 11:32.060
will grow old one by one

11:33.240 --> 11:34.180
and perish.

11:37.510 --> 11:39.180
It's so cruel.

11:43.120 --> 11:44.500
You'll stay with me, won't you?

12:15.390 --> 12:16.800
My time has come, too.

12:23.320 --> 12:24.690
But the title of Dragon Deity

12:25.000 --> 12:26.020
remains a faith

12:26.600 --> 12:28.210
as well as a huge burden.

12:30.030 --> 12:31.180
It's been a century.

12:31.670 --> 12:33.660
Things must have been hard for him.

12:35.600 --> 12:36.570
Has he changed?

12:37.750 --> 12:38.300
He...

12:39.240 --> 12:40.570
is somehow different now.

12:41.840 --> 12:42.840
He's no longer

12:42.840 --> 12:44.090
that simple little fox.

12:45.510 --> 12:47.090
His heart grew much heavier.

12:48.150 --> 12:49.540
His eyes were shrouded,

12:50.720 --> 12:51.970
impossible to see through.

12:53.480 --> 12:54.380
Is that so?

12:56.150 --> 12:57.810
That's why I came to see you.

12:58.910 --> 12:59.810
Ji Ling was haunted

13:00.150 --> 13:01.060
by his inner demon

13:01.480 --> 13:02.420
and fell unconscious.

13:03.870 --> 13:04.730
Inner demon?

13:06.120 --> 13:06.850
Bai Ze said

13:09.630 --> 13:12.140
that it's a demon transformed from your dragon scale,

13:12.910 --> 13:13.810
called Lonescale.

13:15.240 --> 13:16.060
Sorry.

13:16.750 --> 13:18.020
I can't help Ji Ling.

13:19.080 --> 13:20.150
No one in the world

13:20.150 --> 13:21.610
can defeat a Lonescale,

13:22.320 --> 13:23.570
except for Ji Ling himself.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.690
Because a Lonescale

13:26.360 --> 13:27.300
is also a dragon.

13:29.630 --> 13:30.540
Only dragons

13:31.840 --> 13:33.300
can kill a dragon.

13:34.360 --> 13:35.210
That's right.

13:36.440 --> 13:38.500
Destiny loves to play tricks.

13:39.240 --> 13:40.140
If I could

13:41.670 --> 13:42.930
trust him more

13:43.270 --> 13:44.500
and read his mind earlier,

13:45.510 --> 13:46.330
perhaps he wouldn't

13:47.550 --> 13:49.210
be controlled by his inner demon.

13:50.270 --> 13:52.180
He dressed up as the Dragon Deity.

13:52.480 --> 13:53.850
Since ancient times,

13:54.200 --> 13:55.970
fancy attire has always been a shackle.

13:56.120 --> 13:57.570
My intuition tells me

13:58.150 --> 13:59.420
that Wu Shiguang

13:59.510 --> 14:00.420
is not a bad guy.

14:02.480 --> 14:03.540
That low-rank weasel demon

14:03.540 --> 14:05.060
only stole a gown.

14:05.150 --> 14:07.020
But he captured him for a reward.

14:07.480 --> 14:08.450
How is he not bad?

14:09.200 --> 14:11.020
He was trying to save that weasel demon.

14:12.030 --> 14:13.610
That weasel lacked cultivation.

14:13.910 --> 14:15.380
With his current level of power,

14:15.720 --> 14:17.210
he could only wear plain clothes.

14:17.910 --> 14:19.570
Silk and satin would be

14:19.840 --> 14:20.720
too much for him.

14:20.960 --> 14:21.930
He would die.

14:22.550 --> 14:23.780
I had no idea.

14:25.320 --> 14:26.610
Well then, your clothes

14:26.840 --> 14:28.300
are so gorgeous.

14:28.510 --> 14:29.730
Can you handle it?

14:57.840 --> 14:59.690
He wore the clothes of the Dragon Deity

15:00.750 --> 15:02.320
and had to put up

15:02.320 --> 15:03.570
with endless loneliness.

15:12.270 --> 15:15.620
I feel much better these days.

15:16.000 --> 15:18.060
I want to visit my hometown.

15:18.840 --> 15:20.500
My parents' tomb

15:20.750 --> 15:22.810
hasn't been swept for quite a while.

15:33.550 --> 15:37.180
Aging and seriously wounded beasts

15:38.000 --> 15:40.900
always go alone to the hidden caves in the forest

15:41.840 --> 15:45.180
at the end of their lives.

15:45.720 --> 15:47.240
They don't want their kin

15:47.240 --> 15:49.140
to witness their death.

15:49.440 --> 15:52.970
That's their last pride.

15:57.840 --> 15:59.140
Stop looking for me.

16:00.720 --> 16:02.570
I don't want you

16:03.080 --> 16:05.300
to see my ruined look.

16:07.860 --> 16:09.300
♪Black and white, they say♪

16:09.740 --> 16:12.220
♪Love and hate just twist and fade...♪

16:12.240 --> 16:16.730
Think of it as a final goodbye.

16:18.140 --> 16:20.380
♪Whose regret♪

16:20.660 --> 16:22.860
♪Calls out my name?♪

16:23.260 --> 16:27.060
♪Chasing shadows, I slip away...♪

16:27.080 --> 16:28.500
I didn't achieve anything

16:29.270 --> 16:32.690
I've ever wanted to achieve

16:34.200 --> 16:36.810
throughout my life.

16:37.270 --> 16:39.060
I gained nothing.

16:40.840 --> 16:43.210
I failed as an older brother.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.210
Little fox.

16:48.000 --> 16:49.660
I have to go now.

16:50.910 --> 16:51.930
You shouldered

16:52.870 --> 16:55.660
so much burden for me in this life.

16:56.840 --> 16:58.900
I owe you way too much.

16:59.440 --> 17:01.780
I can't atone for my sins now.

17:04.030 --> 17:04.810
Child.

17:05.790 --> 17:08.220
You are kind and pure.

17:09.440 --> 17:11.020
But if there is an afterlife,

17:11.960 --> 17:12.980
I hope

17:13.680 --> 17:15.780
you can be selfish.

17:18.020 --> 17:20.180
♪Watch the sunset♪

17:20.540 --> 17:22.660
♪Burning bright unceasingly♪

17:23.020 --> 17:27.140
♪That touch of red remembers me♪

17:27.980 --> 17:32.700
♪I long for someone to remember me♪

17:33.020 --> 17:38.500
♪I just need you to remember me♪

17:54.310 --> 17:54.980
It's getting cold.

17:55.480 --> 17:56.890
Let me grab you a gown.

18:50.750 --> 18:52.090
Master Chi Wen.

18:54.400 --> 18:56.020
My time has come.

18:59.310 --> 19:01.540
May I be so shameless

19:01.920 --> 19:03.570
as to ask you for one thing,

19:04.920 --> 19:05.890
please?

19:08.070 --> 19:08.610
I'm listening.

19:13.720 --> 19:15.260
For so many years,

19:17.400 --> 19:19.890
I've been by your side.

19:24.110 --> 19:26.330
I only see my wife and child

19:29.960 --> 19:34.300
on New Year's Eve.

19:38.590 --> 19:39.980
I take pride in my devotion

19:41.350 --> 19:43.060
to the Shilin Sect.

19:44.550 --> 19:46.090
However,

19:48.000 --> 19:49.850
I feel guilty to my family.

19:53.030 --> 19:54.740
My child wrote to say

19:57.720 --> 19:58.700
that his mother

20:02.480 --> 20:04.370
doesn't have many days left.

20:13.510 --> 20:14.130
You want me

20:15.680 --> 20:17.060
to save your wife?

20:17.720 --> 20:18.170
No.

20:19.720 --> 20:20.650
Master Chi Wen.

20:22.030 --> 20:23.220
I just want you...

20:24.720 --> 20:25.890
I just want you

20:28.440 --> 20:33.130
to grant me another day of health

20:35.440 --> 20:37.460
so that I have the strength

20:38.440 --> 20:40.130
to get out of bed,

20:42.270 --> 20:44.130
walk out of the Shilin Sect,

20:47.030 --> 20:48.980
and see her once again at home.

20:52.750 --> 20:55.370
Can you fulfill my wish?

20:56.270 --> 20:57.610
Master Chi Wen.

21:04.030 --> 21:04.540
I...

21:13.270 --> 21:14.330
I can't help you.

21:31.270 --> 21:32.060
I'm sorry.

21:36.240 --> 21:38.090
I overstepped.

21:38.960 --> 21:40.370
Master Chi Wen.

21:42.440 --> 21:43.810
The Dragon Deity's Power

21:45.000 --> 21:47.500
should be preserved for those who need it more.

21:50.680 --> 21:52.500
I'll take one step ahead

21:54.920 --> 21:56.650
and wait for her in the other world.

22:00.720 --> 22:02.060
Master Dragon Deity.

22:03.790 --> 22:06.300
I'm so proud

22:08.400 --> 22:13.060
to be able to serve by your side.

22:48.240 --> 22:49.020
I'm sorry.

24:11.200 --> 24:12.220
Yuan Wuhuo

24:13.270 --> 24:13.810
died.

24:17.400 --> 24:18.300
Ye Daoxuan

24:18.640 --> 24:19.330
died, too.

24:24.510 --> 24:25.260
They both

24:30.510 --> 24:31.220
left me.

24:34.960 --> 24:36.460
I don't have the Dragon Deity's Power.

24:37.590 --> 24:38.540
I'm an imposter.

24:41.270 --> 24:42.700
I can't fulfill

24:42.790 --> 24:44.260
anyone's wishes.

24:46.270 --> 24:46.740
Nor can I

24:50.720 --> 24:52.500
keep anyone around.

25:19.160 --> 25:21.020
No one can keep me company forever.

25:24.880 --> 25:25.940
Maybe

25:30.030 --> 25:31.610
this will set me free.

26:28.550 --> 26:29.410
Don't be sad.

26:30.550 --> 26:31.300
Don't cry.

26:32.750 --> 26:34.540
I will always be with you.

26:39.070 --> 26:39.980
Don't be sad.

26:40.750 --> 26:41.780
Don't cry.

26:42.640 --> 26:44.220
I will always be with you.

26:51.110 --> 26:52.610
Don't be sad.

26:52.720 --> 26:53.610
Don't cry.

26:55.030 --> 26:56.940
I will always be with you.

26:59.030 --> 27:00.130
Don't be sad.

27:01.000 --> 27:01.810
Don't cry.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.810
I will always be with you.

27:08.640 --> 27:09.980
- Wu. - Don't be sad.

27:10.070 --> 27:11.260
Don't cry.

27:12.200 --> 27:12.760
Is that you?

27:12.760 --> 27:14.540
I will always be with you.

27:16.000 --> 27:16.780
Wu.

27:19.070 --> 27:20.170
Don't be sad.

27:20.750 --> 27:21.570
Don't cry.

27:22.510 --> 27:24.460
I will always be with you.

28:06.640 --> 28:07.700
Who are you?

28:09.030 --> 28:10.090
I'm Lonescale,

28:11.110 --> 28:12.810
the loneliness residing in you,

28:13.510 --> 28:14.410
your inner demon.

28:16.070 --> 28:17.220
I am you.

28:24.960 --> 28:26.890
Lu Wuyi severed her spiritual tail

28:27.750 --> 28:28.940
and fainted from the pain.

28:29.550 --> 28:30.370
Her spiritual tail

28:30.960 --> 28:32.260
corresponds to the eyes.

28:33.960 --> 28:34.740
What?

28:35.790 --> 28:36.940
Why did she sever her tail?

28:38.790 --> 28:40.410
She followed your soul

28:41.440 --> 28:42.700
back in time.

28:43.750 --> 28:45.300
To see everything,

28:45.880 --> 28:47.940
she had to attach herself to someone

28:48.920 --> 28:50.170
or something.

28:53.880 --> 28:54.540
Back then,

28:56.440 --> 28:58.020
I only had Yuan Wuhuo

28:59.110 --> 29:00.090
and Ye Daoxuan around.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.130
Who was she?

29:06.830 --> 29:08.610
Don't you already know the answer?

29:12.590 --> 29:13.500
Don't be sad.

29:14.550 --> 29:15.370
Don't cry.

29:16.750 --> 29:18.330
I will always be with you.

29:20.640 --> 29:21.570
Don't be sad.

29:22.400 --> 29:23.260
Don't cry.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.460
I will always be with you.

