I will always be with you.

29:47.790 --> 29:48.810
Don't be sad.

29:50.640 --> 29:51.540
Don't cry.

29:52.920 --> 29:54.500
I will always be with you.

29:59.510 --> 30:00.220
My little fox.

30:06.070 --> 30:06.780
It was her.

30:09.920 --> 30:11.260
It's always been her.

30:16.590 --> 30:18.410
Let's reciprocate.

30:19.030 --> 30:21.700
Call me Wu from now on.

30:22.590 --> 30:23.220
Wu.

30:24.440 --> 30:25.410
The cry of a fox.

30:25.720 --> 30:26.500
Wu.

30:27.440 --> 30:29.570
It has the same name.

30:30.790 --> 30:32.060
It turns out that my Wu

30:33.720 --> 30:35.220
has always been my Wu.

30:44.160 --> 30:45.170
Master Daoxuan.

31:04.640 --> 31:06.060
Since you won't save him,

31:06.830 --> 31:08.020
you shall die too.

31:27.140 --> 31:29.180
♪Watch the daylight♪

31:29.620 --> 31:31.860
♪Slowly hiding the moon from sight♪

31:32.380 --> 31:36.580
♪See dewdrops swaying in a dream tonight♪

31:38.020 --> 31:39.020
♪My beloved♪

31:39.380 --> 31:43.140
♪Holds flowers, waiting through the pouring rain♪

31:43.660 --> 31:48.700
♪No words, no questions♪

31:49.660 --> 31:54.300
♪The lovestruck fear not pity, but love laid bare♪

31:54.860 --> 31:59.500
♪Let love and hate be carved into my bones...♪

32:02.310 --> 32:04.130
It's so inconvenient to be a human.

32:07.000 --> 32:08.610
I can't even leave marks.

32:12.220 --> 32:14.020
♪The wind carries her far away♪

32:14.100 --> 32:15.420
♪Back to the past♪

32:15.580 --> 32:17.700
♪Back to when we were young♪

32:17.780 --> 32:22.300
♪Back to his side to see him once more♪

32:23.460 --> 32:25.180
♪May old grudges be cleared away♪

32:25.300 --> 32:26.580
♪May new dreams come true♪

32:26.700 --> 32:29.940
♪People with obsessions...♪

32:31.510 --> 32:32.170
Thank you.

32:34.300 --> 32:36.620
♪We count down to tomorrow♪

32:36.980 --> 32:39.340
♪Life and death beyond the distant snowy mountains♪

32:39.420 --> 32:42.700
♪Silent and wordless, on opposite shores♪

32:42.860 --> 32:44.940
♪We bow to eternity...♪

32:45.400 --> 32:45.810
Here.

32:46.880 --> 32:47.540
Have some too.

32:48.220 --> 32:50.580
♪But can't act along in this play...♪

32:50.590 --> 32:52.060
I left oil on your hands.

32:52.310 --> 32:52.780
It's fine.

32:53.070 --> 32:54.130
I'll wash you later.

32:56.660 --> 32:59.180
♪Let's go back in time♪

32:59.540 --> 33:01.820
♪Snow piled high by the window♪

33:01.900 --> 33:05.180
♪Under sparks of fireworks, we♪

33:05.300 --> 33:07.500
♪Smiled through tears so sweet♪

33:07.620 --> 33:10.700
♪You said you'd find a little corner♪

33:10.740 --> 33:13.020
♪And give me ten thousand wildflowers♪

33:13.060 --> 33:18.140
♪Softly telling me you'd stay with me forever...♪

33:18.160 --> 33:18.780
You are

33:19.240 --> 33:20.500
a little fox.

33:21.200 --> 33:22.370
You can't be furless.

33:23.110 --> 33:23.980
A bald fox

33:24.270 --> 33:25.700
will be mocked.

33:26.380 --> 33:30.460
♪Flowers blooming far and wide...♪

33:30.480 --> 33:31.610
I'll be hairless.

33:31.920 --> 33:32.740
Getting bald.

33:32.740 --> 33:38.540
♪How sweetly we smile♪

33:38.550 --> 33:40.740
I am a little fox without a name.

33:41.750 --> 33:42.330
But

33:42.960 --> 33:44.130
my little fox

33:44.640 --> 33:45.890
must have a name.

33:46.830 --> 33:48.200
Foxes cry like

33:48.200 --> 33:49.610
Wu...

33:50.200 --> 33:51.740
So I'll call you

33:53.310 --> 33:54.020
Wu.

33:56.830 --> 33:57.300
Wu.

33:57.880 --> 34:00.090
Wu.

34:01.310 --> 34:01.940
Yelp.

34:03.200 --> 34:03.740
Yelp.

34:04.510 --> 34:05.540
Yelp for me.

34:06.510 --> 34:07.220
Yelp.

34:09.160 --> 34:09.700
So naughty.

34:10.550 --> 34:11.020
I'll spank you.

34:11.880 --> 34:12.860
Yelp.

34:13.320 --> 34:13.860
Come on.

34:22.650 --> 34:24.580
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

34:27.020 --> 34:29.060
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

34:37.650 --> 34:40.140
♪Don't be sad♪

34:40.140 --> 34:41.860
♪Through every yesterday♪

34:41.940 --> 34:44.460
♪Don't you cry...♪

34:44.550 --> 34:45.290
It hurts.

34:46.420 --> 34:53.860
♪I'll always stay with you♪

34:55.020 --> 34:57.580
♪Don't be sad♪

34:57.610 --> 34:59.300
♪Through every lonely night♪

34:59.380 --> 35:01.820
♪Don't you cry♪

35:01.900 --> 35:03.700
♪Through the darkest nights...♪

35:05.000 --> 35:05.570
It hurts.

35:14.110 --> 35:16.090
I can't go on fooling around.

35:17.190 --> 35:18.460
It's time to grow up.

35:19.670 --> 35:20.210
Goodbye.

35:21.140 --> 35:25.620
♪I'll always stay with you...♪

35:25.630 --> 35:26.610
I'll miss you.

35:27.380 --> 35:29.260
♪Stay with you♪

35:30.740 --> 35:34.860
♪See the daylight wrapped in silver light♪

35:35.980 --> 35:38.860
♪Black turns white with time passing by♪

35:39.300 --> 35:44.020
♪She holds a flower, counts the seasons slow♪

35:44.500 --> 35:47.020
♪Waiting for stone to bloom♪

35:47.380 --> 35:51.340
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

35:51.820 --> 35:55.900
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

35:56.180 --> 35:59.140
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

36:00.020 --> 36:04.420
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

36:04.900 --> 36:08.740
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

36:09.180 --> 36:13.060
♪Your sunrise fades into my gray♪

36:13.540 --> 36:16.940
♪You left behind your final words♪

36:17.340 --> 36:22.060
♪And every word became a scar♪

36:22.340 --> 36:26.220
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

36:26.780 --> 36:30.820
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

36:31.100 --> 36:34.740
♪I call for you, my only one♪

36:35.260 --> 36:42.180
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

36:42.190 --> 36:43.170
Don't be sad.

36:44.190 --> 36:44.980
Don't cry.

36:46.360 --> 36:47.860
I will always be with you.

36:47.860 --> 36:49.580
