36:50.400 --> 36:51.340
Don't be sad.

36:52.110 --> 36:53.130
Don't cry.

36:53.920 --> 36:55.500
I will always be with you.

36:56.510 --> 36:58.060
I will always be with you.

37:03.000 --> 37:03.540
Wu.

37:06.280 --> 37:07.210
Is that you?

37:08.800 --> 37:10.060
Don't be sad.

37:10.190 --> 37:11.210
Don't cry.

37:12.320 --> 37:14.170
I will always be with you.

37:16.400 --> 37:17.650
