37:20.510 --> 37:22.380
I will always be with you.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.540
Don't be sad.

37:27.030 --> 37:27.980
Don't cry.

37:29.360 --> 37:31.210
I will always be with you.

37:34.840 --> 37:37.060
I will always be with you.

37:38.510 --> 37:39.730
Don't be sad.

37:40.190 --> 37:40.940
Don't cry.

37:44.920 --> 37:46.610
The past can't be changed.

37:47.320 --> 37:48.900
Trapped in this doll,

37:49.440 --> 37:50.820
she had to sever her spiritual tail

37:51.400 --> 37:52.980
and unleash all her power

37:53.320 --> 37:54.650
to make a faint sound

37:55.110 --> 37:57.130
through that doll to stop you

37:57.480 --> 37:58.900
from committing suicide.

38:00.230 --> 38:02.730
She is not only my moon,

38:05.960 --> 38:07.070
but she has also

38:07.070 --> 38:08.690
always been my little fox.

38:33.710 --> 38:34.820
After that,

38:35.550 --> 38:37.480
you had a little talking fox

38:37.480 --> 38:38.650
keeping you company

38:39.190 --> 38:40.340
and you were no longer lonely.

38:41.360 --> 38:43.170
You gave up the idea of suicide

38:43.590 --> 38:44.500
and gathered the courage

38:45.630 --> 38:47.770
to become the Dragon Deity step by step.

38:48.880 --> 38:50.020
But the fox doll

38:51.000 --> 38:52.340
never spoke again.

38:54.590 --> 38:56.090
You told people about it,

38:56.710 --> 38:58.170
but nobody believed it.

39:01.150 --> 39:02.500
How can a rag doll

39:02.840 --> 39:03.770
comfort you?

39:04.230 --> 39:05.540
Don't tell me it can talk.

39:06.110 --> 39:07.170
It really talks.

39:10.230 --> 39:10.860
After that,

39:11.800 --> 39:13.290
you created Ji Ling

39:13.400 --> 39:14.650
with the spell of Severed Silk.

39:15.320 --> 39:16.900
You gave him the little fox

39:17.150 --> 39:18.860
and sent him out to wander the world.

39:20.280 --> 39:22.690
Then he met Lu Wuyi.

39:24.360 --> 39:25.610
The universe

39:26.030 --> 39:27.460
is vast and exquisite.

39:28.280 --> 39:29.340
Even I find it hard

39:30.230 --> 39:31.900
to perceive everything.

39:33.190 --> 39:33.900
It turns out

39:35.840 --> 39:37.250
the beginning of the story

39:39.030 --> 39:40.840
has already

39:40.840 --> 39:42.420
been altered by Wu.

39:45.110 --> 39:46.770
Lu Wuyi once asked me

39:47.480 --> 39:49.570
why I would help her go back in time.

39:51.110 --> 39:51.770
I said

39:52.190 --> 39:53.610
I wasn't helping her.

39:54.550 --> 39:55.820
The person I wanted to help

39:58.000 --> 39:58.690
was you.

40:00.400 --> 40:01.290
Your ending

40:01.840 --> 40:04.020
was never to die by your own hand,

40:05.150 --> 40:07.380
nor to sacrifice yourself to that drought.

40:10.110 --> 40:11.500
The end of your life

40:13.110 --> 40:14.210
has always been

40:16.880 --> 40:18.250
to be devoured by me.

40:21.280 --> 40:22.610
We must go back in time

40:23.000 --> 40:24.290
to keep you from loneliness

40:25.920 --> 40:28.130
so that I never come to life.

40:29.630 --> 40:30.210
That is

40:31.190 --> 40:32.860
the only way to change your fate.

40:37.480 --> 40:39.730
Why would you sacrifice yourself

40:41.440 --> 40:42.460
to save me?

40:44.510 --> 40:46.170
Because you are a kind person.

40:47.510 --> 40:48.730
But for a hundred years,

40:49.840 --> 40:51.730
no one in this world has truly loved you,

40:53.230 --> 40:54.610
or been willing to die for you.

40:55.980 --> 40:57.340
Is there anyone who loves you enough

40:57.400 --> 40:58.540
to die for you?

41:01.440 --> 41:01.900
Is there?

41:07.110 --> 41:08.250
Now there is.

41:09.880 --> 41:10.540
She loves you enough

41:11.960 --> 41:13.540
to die for you.

41:15.840 --> 41:16.540
So,

41:17.110 --> 41:18.570
I should disappear.

41:20.150 --> 41:21.090
But

41:22.030 --> 41:23.380
the ending is written.

41:24.440 --> 41:27.170
This is too cruel for you.

41:30.400 --> 41:32.090
She only exists

41:33.150 --> 41:34.500
because of Jiu Ying.

41:35.630 --> 41:36.900
Once Jiu Ying dies,

41:37.440 --> 41:38.540
she will also perish.

41:40.840 --> 41:42.650
But the meaning of your existence

41:43.760 --> 41:45.570
is to annihilate Jiu Ying.

41:48.320 --> 41:49.820
The last Dragon Deity's Power

41:49.880 --> 41:50.690
in this world

41:52.110 --> 41:53.380
has been destroyed.

41:56.590 --> 41:57.650
I don't have to

41:59.840 --> 42:01.210
reach the end.

42:01.800 --> 42:03.090
I used to be a dragon scale.

42:03.760 --> 42:04.340
Therefore,

42:04.800 --> 42:05.770
I carry

42:06.150 --> 42:08.770
the last Dragon Deity's Power in this world.

42:10.510 --> 42:12.290
You can use it to kill Jiu Ying

42:12.960 --> 42:14.460
or to save Lu Wuyi.

42:15.760 --> 42:17.090
This final decision

42:19.480 --> 42:20.940
is up to you.

42:22.150 --> 42:24.500
Jiu Ying sent her to you

42:25.280 --> 42:27.210
to make you fall in love with her

42:28.670 --> 42:30.820
so that you would struggle

42:31.190 --> 42:32.900
between love and duty.

42:36.610 --> 42:38.900
This is what it means to be the fated one.

42:41.110 --> 42:42.420
Between you and her,

42:44.400 --> 42:46.060
one must live,

42:47.550 --> 42:48.500
and one shall perish.

43:20.340 --> 43:21.170
Commander Li.

43:22.030 --> 43:22.900
It's so late.

43:23.070 --> 43:23.940
Why are you here?

43:24.840 --> 43:26.170
I want to see Master Dragon Deity.

43:28.710 --> 43:29.690
Master Dragon Deity

43:30.030 --> 43:30.940
is in the Scale Cave.

43:31.760 --> 43:33.250
Go ahead, please.

44:06.630 --> 44:09.250
I won't let you

44:10.030 --> 44:13.090
hurt Master Dragon Deity.

44:13.480 --> 44:15.650
You are just like your grandfather

44:15.760 --> 44:16.770
Ye Daoxuan.

44:17.920 --> 44:19.570
You'd protect him

44:19.920 --> 44:21.570
at the cost of your lives.

45:09.440 --> 45:10.340
Why did you come here?

45:13.710 --> 45:14.730
To kill him.

45:16.070 --> 45:18.860
The fourth Dragon Deity's Power has been destroyed.

45:20.190 --> 45:22.650
Wu Shiguang can never transform into a dragon.

45:23.360 --> 45:24.340
And Ji Ling

45:24.630 --> 45:26.170
will remain

45:26.190 --> 45:27.570
a false deity,

45:29.400 --> 45:31.290
suffering loneliness forever.

45:32.400 --> 45:34.420
What a cruel fate.

45:35.630 --> 45:37.770
I must set him free.

45:50.760 --> 45:51.770
Triple-flower paints the day.

45:51.880 --> 45:53.020
All things live and perish.

45:53.760 --> 45:55.170
Before me, all becomes clear.

45:59.400 --> 46:00.020
Break!

46:19.760 --> 46:21.730
You're actually using

46:21.920 --> 46:25.340
the demon power preserved for the inner core.

46:26.590 --> 46:28.020
Do you have a death wish?

46:29.280 --> 46:30.340
My life is yours.

46:31.760 --> 46:32.460
But he

46:34.440 --> 46:36.020
must remain alive.

48:20.360 --> 48:21.060
Bai Ze.

48:21.510 --> 48:23.540
Do you think you can beat me

48:23.760 --> 48:25.290
with your petty tricks?

48:30.190 --> 48:30.940
Ye Changsheng.

48:31.400 --> 48:32.090
Well done.

48:38.000 --> 48:39.460
What did you do?

48:40.360 --> 48:42.060
Take my Purple Lightning Chain.

48:43.630 --> 48:44.820
If you see Yuan Wuhuo,

48:45.190 --> 48:45.940
find a way

48:46.030 --> 48:47.460
to merge this with his blade.

48:56.550 --> 48:57.980
Young men of the Shilin Sect

48:59.230 --> 49:00.460
use faith as shields

49:00.840 --> 49:01.860
and courage as spears

49:02.280 --> 49:04.130
to protect the Dragon Deity and the world

49:04.710 --> 49:05.980
until the last minute.

49:07.400 --> 49:08.290
Ye Daoxuan.

49:10.550 --> 49:11.460
Ye Mingshan.

49:13.230 --> 49:14.130
Ye Changsheng.

49:17.480 --> 49:18.730
The devotion to the Shilin Sect

49:18.800 --> 49:19.650
lives on.

49:21.150 --> 49:23.460
Thus, light and hope will never leave this world.

49:25.230 --> 49:25.980
Yuan Wuhuo.

49:27.510 --> 49:28.420
Your sins

49:29.320 --> 49:31.130
end with me today.

51:17.590 --> 51:18.500
Little fox.

51:21.110 --> 51:22.420
I have to go.

51:24.030 --> 51:25.570
I hope you don't

51:28.150 --> 51:29.420
feel lonely again.

51:31.580 --> 51:34.660
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

51:34.980 --> 51:37.820
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

51:38.180 --> 51:40.980
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

51:41.140 --> 51:43.860
♪As I drift farther away♪

51:44.380 --> 51:47.300
♪I won't wipe my tears dry♪

51:47.660 --> 51:50.460
♪Afraid the sorrow fades too light♪

51:54.180 --> 51:56.620
♪No more longing♪

52:02.400 --> 52:03.650
The fifth gem.

52:05.880 --> 52:06.610
Lonescale.

52:30.660 --> 52:34.060
♪The old home's new windows have changed♪

52:34.500 --> 52:37.780
♪A puppy barks to welcome the dawn♪

52:38.340 --> 52:44.620
♪The deceased sent new clothes in a dream♪

52:46.700 --> 52:50.060
♪Tired and rushing, youth in a hurry♪

52:50.540 --> 52:53.860
♪My heart stays in that old place♪

52:54.260 --> 52:57.300
♪Singing about dreams, singing about light♪

52:57.780 --> 53:01.300
♪Calling me to the distance♪

53:17.740 --> 53:21.820
♪Who will meet♪

53:22.340 --> 53:27.460
♪That grown-up me? Under stars and the hanging moon♪

53:27.980 --> 53:33.820
♪Safe and happy, no trouble, no harm♪

53:50.420 --> 53:53.980
♪Quick footsteps, racing heart♪

53:54.500 --> 53:57.700
♪Busy running through the snow♪

53:58.220 --> 54:04.540
♪The person in my dream glows by the river♪

54:06.420 --> 54:10.060
♪The night wind is cold, my tears hot♪

54:10.580 --> 54:13.300
♪The one I love is ahead♪

54:13.820 --> 54:16.780
♪My homeland, my strange land♪

54:17.300 --> 54:20.860
♪Both lit by fireworks♪

54:37.620 --> 54:41.460
♪Who still remembers♪

54:42.060 --> 54:47.140
♪The child I used to be? Under the sparks of fireworks♪

54:47.660 --> 54:53.660
♪I gently clasped my hands, wishing for a life free of harm♪
